Class FullExperimentEnricher

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.impl.AbstractMIEnricher<Experiment>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExperimentEnricher, MIEnricher<Experiment>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FullExperimentUpdater, ImexExperimentUpdater

    public class FullExperimentEnricher
extends MinimalExperimentEnricher
    Provides full enrichment of experiment. - enrich minimal properties of experiment. See MinimalExperimentEnricher - enrich xrefs - enrich annotations - enrich confidences - enrich variable parameters
    Since:
    13/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
